🤖 Customer Intelligence System: RFM, Clustering & Strategy Engine

This project presents an end-to-end Customer Analytics & Intelligence System that transforms raw transactional data into actionable business strategies.

It combines data analysis, machine learning, and business logic to not only segment customers but also recommend what actions a business should take next.

🚀 Project Overview

The project is divided into four key stages:

📊 Part 1: RFM Analysis → Understand customer behavior
🤖 Part 2: K-Means Clustering → Segment customers
📈 Part 3: Cluster Insights → Analyze segment performance
🧠 Part 4: Customer Strategy Engine → Generate business actions
🎯 Objective

To build a system that:

Segments customers based on purchasing behavior
Identifies high-value and low-value customers
Estimates customer lifetime value (CLTV)
Recommends personalized business strategies
Supports data-driven decision-making
